      <title>万洲国际预计猪肉需求疲软导致中国生猪价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/wh-group-sees-china-s-pig-prices-dropping-amid-weak-pork-demand</link>
